Text: Thanks a lot! Sprints are my favourite kind of competition!
I encoded this and the 2 IBU races all together - that took about 9 hours. The encoding finished about 1am this morning.

I missed this race:
FIS World Cup Cross-Country Team Sprint Dusseldorf (6th Dec 2009)

It wasn't marked as "live". It started at 5:30pm GMT and lasted 30 minutes - obviously recorded from earlier on.
Tank you! Do you have the sprint from dusseldorf from earlier years ?
